s model/process model instance migration</li>\\r\\n\\t<li>CAVR and other audit compliance (audit trail? non-repudiation?)</li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Performance, scalability, manageability and other ususal -ilities JMX/SNMP support for ITSM etc.)\\r\\n</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n(not a complete list)\\r\\n\\r\\nIBM Fellow joke \\\"you can't swing a cat around in a room w/o hitting a workflow engine\\\".\"}" localhost:9940/element
